 <h1 id="students_show">Student Overview Page Help</h1>
 <p>The <em>student overview</em> page provides an intuitive graphical summary of one student&#8217;s academic performance in all classes over the course of a marking period. By default the page shows the current marking period, but if you want to see how a student did during an earlier marking period, you can. Below is what the first line on the <em>student overview</em> page would look like for Kurt the example student during the third marking period (the 3 is the only number that is not a link). If you wanted to look at marking period 2 (if this was a real student), you would just click the 2.</p>
