<p>The grade progression charts show the student&#8217;s grade in each class over time. Kurt the example student started off well with a 90% on the first assignment of the marking period, and had a 95% average after the second, but then things started to go wrong, and he dropped to 60% before bringing his average back up to almost 70.</p>
<h2 class="clear">Other Information</h2>
<p>In the sidebar of the <em>student overview</em> page you can find out the last time the student and his parents logged in, links to edit the student&#8217;s account, and a link to see a class level overview of all of the student&#8217;s classes.</p>
